data.description: The Bellvue is a single-story with 3 beds, 2 baths & 1415 sqft of living space. The spacious kitchen is open to the dining room & large family room. The kitchen features stainless appliances & granite counters. The owner's suite is off the family room & has a huge walk in closet & large walk in shower. The secondary bedrooms have large walk in closets. Full yard professional irrigation & landscaping with Bermuda sod. Room measurements are estimates and buyer to verify.
